data.title: Banking, Financial & General Awareness 2015 For Upcoming Exams
data.meta_description: Banking, Financial & General Awareness 2015 for Upcoming Exams - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides an overview of topics related to banking awareness, financial awareness, and general awareness that would be helpful for exams like IBPS RRB, IBPS PO, IBPS Clerk, and SBI Clerk. It includes chapters on the Indian financial system, the banking system structure in India, payment and settlement systems, regulatory bodies, concepts in the Indian economy and understanding the budget. The document aims to cover basic but important concepts for upcoming banking exams through its various chapters. It also provides website and social media details for additional resources.
